name: ActRelationshipEndsConcurrentWithStart
title: ActRelationshipEndsConcurrentWithStart
description: The source Act ends when the target act starts (i.e. if we say "ActOne ECWS ActTwo", it means that ActOne ends when ActTwo starts, therefore ActOne is the source and ActTwo is the target).
